クラス
org.gjt.sp.jedit.PluginJAR の使用

PluginJAR を使用しているパッケージ
org.gjt.sp.jedit This package contains jEdit's core classes. 
org.gjt.sp.jedit.gui Various GUI controls and dialog boxes. 
org.gjt.sp.jedit.msg EditBus messages. 
 

org.gjt.sp.jedit での PluginJAR の使用
 

PluginJAR として宣言されている org.gjt.sp.jedit のフィールド
 PluginJAR PluginJAR.PluginCacheEntry.plugin
           
 

PluginJAR を返す org.gjt.sp.jedit のメソッド
 PluginJAR EditPlugin.getPluginJAR()
          Returns the JAR file containing this plugin.
 PluginJAR ActionSet.getPluginJAR()
          Return the plugin this action set was loaded from, or null.
static PluginJAR jEdit.getPluginJAR(java.lang.String path)
          Returns the JAR with the specified path name.
static PluginJAR[] jEdit.getPluginJARs()
          Returns an array of installed plugins.
static PluginJAR PluginJAR.load(java.lang.String path, boolean loadDependents)
          Loads a plugin, and its dependent plugins if necessary.
 

PluginJAR 型のパラメータを持つ org.gjt.sp.jedit のメソッド
static PluginJAR.PluginCacheEntry PluginJAR.getPluginCache(PluginJAR plugin)
           
static void ServiceManager.loadServices(PluginJAR plugin, java.net.URL uri, PluginJAR.PluginCacheEntry cache)
          Loads a services.xml file.
static void ServiceManager.registerService(java.lang.String clazz, java.lang.String name, java.lang.String code, PluginJAR plugin)
          Registers a service.
static void jEdit.removePluginJAR(PluginJAR jar, boolean exit)
          Unloads the given plugin JAR with the specified path.
static void ServiceManager.unloadServices(PluginJAR plugin)
          Removes all services belonging to the specified plugin.
 

PluginJAR 型のパラメータを持つ org.gjt.sp.jedit のコンストラクタ
